VAL-INTEGRATION-002.notes:
All documented error codes verified at runtime:
- AUTH_FAILED (401): Invalid credentials returns {code:'AUTH_FAILED', message:'Invalid username or password'}
- INVALID_REQUEST (400): Malformed JSON returns {code:'INVALID_REQUEST', message:'Invalid request body'}
- MISSING_TOKEN (401): No auth header returns {code:'MISSING_TOKEN', message:'Authorization header required'}
- INVALID_TOKEN (401): Invalid token returns {code:'INVALID_TOKEN', message:'Token is invalid or expired'}
- INVALID_TOKEN_FORMAT (401): Non-Bearer header returns {code:'INVALID_TOKEN_FORMAT', message:'Expected Bearer <token>'}
- MISSING_PARAMETER (400): Missing lecture params returns {code:'MISSING_PARAMETER', message:'subject_id and session_id query parameters required'}
- JOB_NOT_FOUND (404): Invalid job ID returns {code:'JOB_NOT_FOUND', message:'Job not found'}
- INVALID_JOB_CONFIG (400): Invalid quality returns {code:'INVALID_JOB_CONFIG', message:'quality must be one of: 144, 450, 720'}

